# Trivy ignore list
#
# CVE IDs listed here are honored by the trivy-action CI scan. Each entry
# mirrors a code-scanning alert that has been reviewed and dismissed in the
# GitHub UI (Settings > Code security > Code scanning alerts). Trivy in CI
# does NOT honor GitHub's dismissal state on its own; without this file the
# Container Scan job fails on each scheduled run with the same CVEs that
# were already triaged.
#
# Add a new entry only after dismissing the corresponding code-scanning
# alert with a "won't fix" rationale. Include the CVE ID, severity, and a
# one-line justification. Re-evaluate entries when the underlying package
# is updated.

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Resolved by package.json overrides; stale container scan will clear
# once the next container rebuild lands.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
